title: Starry Moment
lyrics:
Gakkai ol ttae mada nae mam-eun kung!kung!
Teojil geosman gat-eungeol (teojil geos gat-a)
Neol mollae bol ttaemada nae nun-eun kkamppag
Jakku neoman boyeo naneun ije eotteoghae
Tto tiga nage bukkeuleobge

Nal boneun neoui misoleul bomyeon

Wae mal-eul an halkka? gibun johge mimyohan tteollim

Ij-eul su eobsneun sungan-iya



Seolleneun bam geudae jeo byeol-eul tago naelyeowa

Joh-ahanda naege mal-eul haejullaeyo

Kokkeut-i ganjileobge kkoch hyang-gi doeeo

Neoegelo geudae mam-e bukkeuleowo na



Kkattagkkattag gogael hilkkeumhilkkeum geudael



Neodo neukkyeossjanh-a naui aikeontaeg

Mag tteollyeo wa na eojjeom neon



Ttag johge geulae kkog majge naegen

Seolleneun bam seolleneun na seolleneun uli dul



Eonjena neowana mwonga ilwojil geos gat-eun

Geuleon gibun-i deul-eoss-eo (mwonga teugbyeolhan)

Jogeumssig jogeumssig neoui hyang-giga jit-eojyeo

Dugeungeolimjocha ijeneun Stop!

Neoleul mos bogess-eo



Joh-ahanda ani an handa

Daedab eobsneun kkoch-ipman tteeo

Balam-i bul-eowa neol nae mam-e

Salang-e ppajineun geon han sungan-ilanikka



Wae mal-eul an halkka? gibun johge mimyohan tteollim

Ij-eul su eobsneun sungan-iya



Seolleneun bam geudae jeo byeol-eul tago naelyeowa

Joh-ahanda naege mal-eul haejullaeyo

Kokkeut-i ganjileobge kkoch hyang-gi doeeo

Neoegelo geudae mam-e bukkeuleowo na



Ttag joh-eun ondo ttag joh-eun balam

O unmyeong gat-eun salang naege dagaon geojyo

Ijen pum-e angyeo mal halgeyo

Salanghae

Joh-ahanda naege mal-eul haejullaeyo

Kokkeut-i ganjileobge kkoch hyang-gi doeeo

Kkattagkkattag gogael hilkkeumhilkkeum geudael



Ije neodo naleul bogo aikeontaeg

Mag tteollyeo wa na eojjeom neon



Ttag johge geulae kkog majge naegen

Seolleneun bam seolleneun na seolleneun uli dul
